metadata.name: The Dopest Pot #1
metadata.description: What lies before you is known famously amongst witches as the Crokaine Brew. This fabled brew is an integral and irreplaceable step in the delicate and deliberate manifestation of Tyrol's favourite and most esoteric powdered concoction! Stir the pot for long enough and you're due to find something rather special calcified to its base.
